that we want to take something away from people. We don't.

1091
00:46:16,850 --> 00:46:18,130
我们只是想让那些坏人
We want to make it more difficult

1092
00:46:18,220 --> 00:46:21,060
获取枪支的途径更困难
for dangerous people to buy firearms.

1093
00:46:21,140 --> 00:46:22,510
