不能让极度渴望想要买枪的人
anyone that desperate to get their hands on a gun

1117
00:47:01,270 --> 00:47:03,640
这么容易地得到它
shouldn't be allowed anywhere near one.

1118
00:47:03,770 --> 00:47:06,350
威斯康星总共的核磁共振机器的数量…
The total number of MRI machines in Wisconsin...

1119
