Of an additional $2 million

1127
00:47:21,120 --> 00:47:23,780
会在一年内启用额外的两百万
for the purchase of four brand-new machines

1128
00:47:23,870 --> 00:47:26,360
购买四台全新的机器
within the first year of my next term.

1129
00:47:26,460 --> 00:47:28,200
