They've been tracking us through Wisconsin.

1139
00:47:49,610 --> 00:47:51,440
可能名单上的人 他们都做了审查
They would have had everyone on that list vetted.

1140
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:52,890
你被发现了
You're blown.

1141
00:47:52,980 --> 00:47:54,270
什么意思？
What do you mean?

1142
00:47:54,530 --> 00:47:56,940
也就是说 该启用备用方案了
I mean that it's time for plan B.

1143
00:47:58,660 --> 00:48:03,200
最后一个问题 拉杰·阿玛拉斯卡拉医生
And our final question goes to Dr. Raj Amarasekara.

1144
00:48:03,290 --> 00:48:04,950
希望我没有读错
I hope I'm pronouncing that right.

1145
00:48:05,040 --> 00:48:06,900
来自美国肺学协会
Of the Pulmonary Associates of America.

1146
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:08,240
谢谢
Thank you.

1147
00:48:10,040 --> 00:48:11,160
拉杰·阿玛拉斯卡拉 实际上是一个名叫
Raj Amarasekara is a working actor

1148
00:48:11,210 --> 00:48:12,590
马修·坎塔利亚的演员
named Matthew Kantaria.

1149
