正如你所说
As you have experienced, uh,

1157
00:48:37,150 --> 00:48:39,310
枪支暴力确实是真实存在的问题…
gun violence is a real problem...

1158
00:48:39,660 --> 00:48:40,940
你把我当诱饵？
You decoyed me?

1159
