七篇研究论文 都可以在网上找到
seven research papers, all available online.

1161
00:48:46,620 --> 00:48:47,990
他还有医缘网的账号
He even has a Doximity account.

1162
00:48:48,080 --> 00:48:50,540
…财政负担确实是有的
Financial burden is the fact that

1163
00:48:50,630 --> 00:48:53,210
