年轻人
The young.

1166
00:48:57,840 --> 00:49:00,500
所以我觉得 首要的是
So, I think it's, uh, first and foremost,

1167
00:49:00,590 --> 00:49:05,380
向那些受害者家属表示同情和慰问
to put our sympathies with the families of these victims.

1168
00:49:07,180 --> 00:49:10,600
但是的确 枪支暴力对于我们的医疗系统
But it's true, gun violence puts an enormous strain

1169
00:49:10,690 --> 00:49:14,140
以及其所需的人手 产生了很严重的负担
on our healthcare system and its work force.

1170
00:49:14,860 --> 00:49:16,720
确实是这样的
Absolutely, yes.

1171
00:49:16,820 --> 00:49:19,860
所以我才会全心全意支持
That's why I intend to give my whole-hearted support

1172
00:49:21,240 --> 00:49:22,730
希顿·哈里斯法案
to the Heaton-Harris Bill.

1173
00:49:24,240 --> 00:49:25,700
这叫掩人耳目
And that's a wrap.

1174
00:49:26,580 --> 00:49:29,610
谢谢大家 非常感谢
Thank you. Absolutely, thank you.

1175
00:49:39,260 --> 00:49:40,420
