1187
00:50:04,370 --> 00:50:05,570
稍后我会把细节发给你
I'll forward you the details.

1188
00:50:10,200 --> 00:50:11,240
又是你
You again.

1189
00:50:13,000 --> 00:50:15,660
我还专门打过电话 指名道姓叫他们派马克来
I called them and I specifically asked for Mark.

1190
00:50:16,380 --> 00:50:18,080
那我也专门告诉你 他跑路了
And I specifically told you he skipped town.

1191
00:50:18,800 --> 00:50:20,460
他去哪个代理公司了？
Well, what agency did he move to?

1192
