啊 我们那晚玩得多开心啊
Aww, we had so much fun the other night.

1197
00:50:36,060 --> 00:50:37,650
小姐 你知道门在哪儿
Well, you know where the door is, lady.

1198
00:50:37,770 --> 00:50:38,850
去找你的马克吧
Go run to your Mark.

1199
00:51:20,020 --> 00:51:21,560
