How did you know it was her?

1629
01:09:30,410 --> 01:09:31,690
什么？
Sorry?

1630
01:09:31,780 --> 01:09:33,820
泄密的人 你派人监视辛西娅
The leak, you had Cynthia watched.

1631
01:09:34,120 --> 01:09:35,570
你怎么知道是她？
How did you know it was her?

1632
01:09:36,290 --> 01:09:37,820
我不知道
I didn't.

1633
01:09:39,250 --> 01:09:40,750
