卡尔·斯奈德 我是做银行保险的
Cal Sneider, banking and actuarial.

1636
01:09:47,920 --> 01:09:49,080
我们之前见过
I'm sure we've been introduced,

1637
01:09:49,130 --> 01:09:50,120
