but your name escapes me.

1638
01:09:50,300 --> 01:09:51,760
抱歉 你认错人了
I'm sorry, you have the wrong person.

1639
01:09:52,010 --> 01:09:53,130
我绝对没有
I'm pretty sure I don't.

1640
01:09:53,350 --> 01:09:54,800
我这人认人很准的
Have a good memory for faces.

1641
01:09:55,260 --> 01:09:56,640
像你这么漂亮 我更不会忘了
This one I wouldn't readily forget.

1642
01:09:57,430 --> 01:09:59,090
真的 斯奈德先生
Really, Mr. Sneider,

1643
01:09:59,520 --> 01:10:01,310
你一定是认错人了
I've no idea who you think I am.

1644
01:10:01,440 --> 01:10:02,810
我先走了
Excuse me.

1645
01:10:11,320 --> 01:10:13,030
你知道现在这个时候
Uh-huh. You know we're not really

1646
