It guarantees the right to keep and bear arms.

1724
01:13:00,870 --> 01:13:02,400
是你最近没有好好翻阅吧
Perhaps you haven't read it lately.

1725
01:13:02,540 --> 01:13:03,950
修正案中没有任何
Nothing in the bill

1726
01:13:04,040 --> 01:13:06,900
限制公民买枪及持枪的合法权利
infringes the rights of the people to keep and bear arms.

1727
01:13:07,000 --> 01:13:08,490
第二修正案签署于
The Second Amendment was signed in a time

1728
01:13:08,500 --> 01:13:10,360
一个平均年龄只有三十八岁的年代
where the average life expectancy was 38,

1729
01:13:10,460 --> 01:13:13,040
