is wholly inadequate to solve the problems of the present.

1733
01:13:22,310 --> 01:13:24,170
这不是预演好的辩词 她在干什么？
That's not the rebuttal, what's she doing?

1734
01:13:24,310 --> 01:13:25,670
美国宪法经受住了
The United States Constitution

1735
01:13:25,730 --> 01:13:27,260
时间的考验
has stood the test of time.

1736
01:13:27,350 --> 01:13:31,010
它给公民授予的权利是不可置疑的
It's authored to confer unimpeachable rights,

1737
01:13:31,150 --> 01:13:32,350
