which don't change depending

1738
01:13:32,770 --> 01:13:34,440
时代的变迁而被撼动
on which way the Wind's blowing.

1739
01:13:34,690 --> 01:13:36,400
这种权利也能让别有意图的
It's so authored with the specific intent

1740
01:13:36,490 --> 01:13:37,650
比如全世界
of keeping at bay

1741
01:13:37,740 --> 01:13:39,440
像伊丽莎白·斯隆这种
the Elizabeth Sloanes of this world,

1742
01:13:39,610 --> 01:13:41,480
想拿宪法擦屁股的人干瞪眼
