才找到这位证人的 波斯纳先生
able to locate the witness, Mr. Posner.

2429
01:50:24,690 --> 01:50:25,730
让他们开始
Let it play.

2430
01:50:26,530 --> 01:50:28,190
我能和我的客户谈谈吗？
A moment with my client, please?

2431
01:50:29,030 --> 01:50:30,860
什么情况？罗伯特·福德是谁？
What is this? Who's Robert Forde?

2432
01:50:32,160 --> 01:50:33,620
听着 我可以上诉…
Look, I can make a public appeal...

2433
01:50:33,700 --> 01:50:34,740
赶紧开始吧 该死
Let it play, damn it.

2434
01:50:34,830 --> 01:50:36,910
他们不达目的 是不会罢休的
They're going to get it out there one way or another.

2435
01:50:50,430 --> 01:50:52,710
福德先生 请举起你的右手
Mr. Forde, please raise your right hand.

2436
01:50:54,020 --> 01:50:56,050
你愿意庄严宣誓 你所说的话
Do you solemnly swear that you will tell the truth,

2437
01:50:56,140 --> 01:50:58,050
