What would you say earns you the most income at present?

2444
01:51:22,920 --> 01:51:24,000
我在华盛顿做社交陪同
I work as an escort in D.C.

2445
01:51:29,760 --> 01:51:31,420
你靠和女人睡觉赚钱？
You sleep with women for money?

2446
01:51:32,100 --> 01:51:33,460
我会满足客户的需求
I meet the clients' needs.

2447
01:51:34,470 --> 01:51:35,680
不管是什么样的
Whatever they may be.

2448
01:51:36,720 --> 01:51:39,340
有时 客户可能都不知道她们有什么需求
Sometimes, the client don't even know what they need.

2449
01:51:40,230 --> 01:51:42,060
我的一部分工作就是帮她们解决问题
Part of my job's to figure that out.

2450
01:51:42,150 --> 01:51:43,760
但有时你的工作要求你
But, sometimes, your job entails

2451
01:51:44,440 --> 01:51:46,230
实施性交换取钱财 对吧？
having intercourse for payment?

2452
01:51:47,900 --> 01:51:49,190
是的
Yes, sir.

2453
01:51:49,900 --> 01:51:52,020
你见过伊丽莎白·斯隆吗？
Have you ever met Elizabeth Sloane?

2454
01:51:52,120 --> 01:51:53,650
主席先生 参议院没有权利
Mr. Chairman, the Senate has no business

2455
01:51:53,660 --> 01:51:55,520
