prying into the personal affairs of Miss Sloane.

2456
01:51:55,620 --> 01:51:57,040
拉皮条是一种犯罪行为
Solicitation is a criminal offense.

2457
01:51:57,040 --> 01:51:59,370
这场听证会的作用就在于
It's well within the remit of this hearing

2458
01:51:59,460 --> 01:52:00,790
探讨斯隆女士
to establish whether Miss Sloane

2459
01:52:00,870 --> 01:52:01,910
是否有犯罪行为
has broken any laws.

2460
01:52:02,790 --> 01:52:03,830
福德先生
Mr. Forde.

2461
01:52:04,420 --> 01:52:06,710
你见过斯隆女士吗？
Have you ever met Miss Sloane?

2462
01:52:08,340 --> 01:52:09,370
见过
Yep.

2463
01:52:09,840 --> 01:52:11,380
