都被你拒绝了
whose visits you've been refusing.

2612
02:04:15,360 --> 02:04:16,850
你看上去气色不错
You look good.

2613
02:04:17,690 --> 02:04:19,700
如果你没有老二 监狱不算是个坏地方
Prison's not so bad if you don't have a penis.

2614
02:04:20,200 --> 02:04:22,480
我们不会在别人身上发泄 自己解决就行了
We don't shank each other, we form self-help groups.

2615
02:04:24,030 --> 02:04:25,440
监狱里有卖润唇膏的地方
There's a black market in lip gloss.

2616
