嗯
Hmm.

2617
02:04:27,950 --> 02:04:28,990
为什么同意见我？
Why this time?

2618
02:04:31,420 --> 02:04:32,870
他们告诉我 这次是公事
They told me it was business.

2619
02:04:33,420 --> 02:04:34,700
没错 额…
Yeah. Um...

2620
02:04:35,550 --> 02:04:36,830
关于斯珀林和杜邦的听证会
Now that the Sperling and Dupont hearings

2621
02:04:36,880 --> 02:04:37,910
已经提上了日程
are on the schedule,

2622
02:04:38,050 --> 02:04:39,500
我在帮你申请提前释放
I'm petitioning for an early release.

2623
02:04:40,260 --> 02:04:41,540
你看上去也很精神
You look good, too, by the way.

2624
02:04:42,050 --> 02:04:43,380
谢谢
Thank you.

2625
02:04:44,720 --> 02:04:48,210
你只需要再待四个月 最多六个月
I think we are looking at four, maybe six months.

2626
