跟美国国会大厦的人来个正面对峙
brought the roof of the US Capitol

2629
02:05:02,740 --> 02:05:04,070
结果弄得两败俱伤
crashing down on your head.

2630
02:05:04,990 --> 02:05:07,150
为了什么 就为了一个枪支法案？
For what, a gun bill?

2631
02:05:09,160 --> 02:05:11,450
- 这很有效 不是吗？ - 祝贺你
- Worked, didn't it?  - Well, congrats.

2632
02:05:12,420 --> 02:05:13,830
罪犯现在买枪
Criminals must now endure the hassle

2633
02:05:13,920 --> 02:05:15,660
都只能去黑市买了
of procuring their guns on the black market.

2634
02:05:17,500 --> 02:05:19,120
这样断送自己的前程 真的值得吗？
Was that really worth your career?

2635
02:05:21,670 --> 02:05:23,260
如果你把因为工作而自杀 和断送自己的工作
Career suicide is not so bad when you

2636
02:05:23,430 --> 02:05:26,010
两者进行比较 就不会觉得这有什么大不了了
consider the alternative is suicide by career.

2637
02:05:27,930 --> 02:05:29,090
我的医生会告诉你
My doctor would tell you

2638
02:05:29,640 --> 02:05:31,430
我服刑表现很好的
I've served my interest very well.

2639
02:05:34,190 --> 02:05:35,180
嗯
Hmm.

2640
02:05:38,150 --> 02:05:39,430
谢谢你来看我 丹尼尔
Thanks for coming, Daniel.

2641
02:05:42,150 --> 02:05:43,360
我很好奇
I'm curious.

2642
02:05:46,120 --> 02:05:47,530
你签署的那个文件？
Your little filing snafu?

2643
02:05:49,450 --> 02:05:50,910
你是故意在上面签字的
You filled out that form deliberately.

2644
02:05:51,000 --> 02:05:52,370
那也是你计划的一部分 给他们设下圈套
That was you, throwing them a bone.

2645
02:05:53,660 --> 02:05:55,950
如果没有那个文件 也不会推动他们举办听证会
Without it, they would have nothing to incite the hearing.

2646
02:05:57,170 --> 02:05:59,080
你没有义务回答这个问题
And you're under no obligation to answer that.

2647
02:06:05,340 --> 02:06:06,830
而且整件事你完全没有
And you neglected to mention this

2648
02:06:06,970 --> 02:06:08,130
告诉团队的成员 是因为…
to any of your team because...

2649
02:06:08,180 --> 02:06:09,290
至少需要五年的信任
Five years minimum.

2650
